name: Ocean Star Necklace
description: True to it’s name Ocean Star provides you with the beauty of the ocean and all the jewels it has to offer. It consists of chocolate and almond-coloured faux pearls, exquisite turquoise gemstones and an extremely beautiful Italian Murano Glass-Star with brown, silver and turquoise dustings. Ocean Star is not only spectacular, it is bold, beautiful and empowering. Item#: JN4322 Length: 16 Inches w/ 2.25-inch pendant drop. Gemstone: Turquoise Other: Faux Pearls (brown & almond) Clasp Style: Fish Hook Clasp Metal: Sterling Silver

name: Bella Necklace
description: The Bella necklace is definitely a head-turner and its quartz gemstones radiate with golden perfection. Bella’s unique design allows for a simple knot in the front to hold it together. You’ll certainly feel like a celebrity or supermodel when you wear this piece. Item #: JN4328 Length: 23 Inches Gemstone: Carnelian (Agate) Metal: 14kt Yellow Gold over Sterling Silver. Clasp Style: n/a

name: Butterfly Necklace
description: The Butterfly Necklace seems delicate yet elegant, it’s pure white shells contains the glossy luster of a pearl. And the sparkling smoky-topaz Swarovski Crystals help to accentuate the shimmering Mother-of- Pearl Butterfly-Pendant. Item #: JN4325 Length: 14 3/4 Inches Pendant Gemstone: Brown Mother of Pearl Necklace: White Shells Swarovski Crystal: Colour: Smoky-Topaz Shape: Bi-Cone Size: 8mm Clasp Style: Fish Hook Clasp Metal: 14k Gold over Sterling Silver

name: Love Dust Necklace
description: Love Dust is an eccentric, trendy necklace and it’s the perfect piece to complete your wardrobe. It’s focal points are the Chocolate and Red Heart-shapes designed with Bohemian style natural Bamboo & Wood beads that become smaller as they gravitate to the back of the necklace. Item#: JN4317 Length: 23.5 Inches Components: Natural Bamboo & Wood Beads Colour: Red and Dark Brown Shape: Jumbo Hearts & Circles Clasp Style: Fish Hook Clasp Metal: Sterling Silver

name: Simply Irresistible Necklace
description: Simply Irresistible is a true replica of exquisite grace. Its cascading silver chain is complemented by the beautiful black onyx gemstones that it cradels. Item #: JN4330 Length: 29 1/2 Inches Gemstone: Black Onyx Shape: Round-Balls & Flat-Circles Size 8mm & 15mm Metal: Sterling Silver Chain. Clasp Style: Fish Hook Clasp Metal: Sterling Silver.
